Risk
├── id (UUID)
├── organization_id (FK)
├── title
├── description
├── category (strategic, operational, financial, compliance, technology)
├── owner_id (FK - User)
├── likelihood (1-5)
├── impact (1-5)
├── risk_score (calculated)
├── inherent_risk_score
├── residual_risk_score
├── status (identified, assessing, treating, monitoring, closed)
├── treatment_plan
├── target_closure_date
├── tags (array)
├── created_by (FK - User)
├── created_at
└── updated_at